On Friday, July 26, 2024 at 7:24:39‚ÄØAM UTC-7 PhistucK wrote:&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

&gt; Should this kind of change go through the Chromium/Blink intent process 
&gt; perhaps? Especially given the already indicated breakage?
