MeasurementUsage is measured by the SchedulerYield UseCounter: &lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/popularity#SchedulerYield"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/popularity#SchedulerYield&lt;/a&gt;
