&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Requires code in //chrome?False
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Tracking bug&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=979020"&gt;https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=979020&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; MeasurementUsage is measured by the SchedulerYield UseCounter:
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/popularity#SchedulerYield"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/popularity#SchedulerYield&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Availability expectationInitially available only in Chromium browsers.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Adoption expectationFeature is a key part of optimizing long tasks,
&gt;&gt; which contribute to poor responsiveness:
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://web.dev/articles/optimize-long-tasks"&gt;https://web.dev/articles/optimize-long-tasks&lt;/a&gt;. Several partners are
