WebKit: Shipped/Shipping (&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://developer.apple.com/documentation/safari-release-notes/safari-17-release-notes"&gt;https://developer.apple.com/documentation/safari-release-notes/safari-17-release-notes&lt;/a&gt;) Shipped in Safari version 17
