&gt;&gt; a new compression method for transporting resources over HTTP. Web sites
&gt;&gt; can know the browser support for the new feature by checking
&gt;&gt; `document.createElement('link').relList.supports('dictionary')`.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;
&gt;
