&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-httpbis-compression-dictionary"&gt;https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-httpbis-compression-dictionary&lt;/a&gt;
